		</li><li class="widget widget_text" id="text-488023562"><h3>Mission</h3>			<div class="textwidget">EFF-Austin advocates establishment and protection of digital rights and defense of the wealth of digital information, innovation, and technology. We promote the right of all citizens to communicate and share information without unreasonable constraint. We also advocate the fundamental right to explore, tinker, create, and innovate along the frontier of emerging technologies.
<br /><br />
